title: A Place to Go [1964 - UK] London crime drama
description:
A Place to Go (1964 - UK)

Crime / Drama
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0057415/


Made on location in Bethnal Green, London, England, UK

Amidst the pub sing-songs and bombsites and with slums giving way to high-rise flats, life in Bethnal Green is changing for the Flints. Dad may decide to quit the docks and their daughter wants a new home with her husband and expected baby. Son Ricky is dissatisfied with his lot and is equally eager to get away. Involved with a planned robbery of the cigarette factory where he works, his life becomes even more complicated when he gets involved with the quirky Catherine.
